      <title>宏观对冲基金为勇敢的投资者带来巨额收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/macro-hedge-funds-reward-brave-investors-with-huge-gains-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Nishant Kumar 表示，宏观对冲基金因唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选而获得了巨额回报，愿意承担这些风险的投资者期待 2025 年获得更多收益。“看起来今年是宏观交易者的好年头，”Kumar 在“彭博未平仓合约”上表示。Sonali Basak 的华尔街快讯于周五发布。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-03/macro-hedge-funds-reward-brave-investors-with-huge-gains-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 16:13:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
